{"title":"实体类在Windows程序中的高级应用","uid":"f5b6f740573598b25d3452e0d944c6dc","slug":"实体类在Windows程序中的高级应用","date":"2020-08-15T10:49:36.000Z","updated":"2021-06-03T01:47:18.674Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/实体类在Windows程序中的高级应用.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"实体类在Windows程序中的高级应用\"><a href=\"#实体类在Windows程序中的高级应用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实体类在Windows程序中的高级应用\"></a>实体类在Windows程序中的高级应用</h1><h2 id=\"三层架构下的多表查询\"><a href=\"#三层架构下的多表查询\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三层架构下的多表查询\"></a>三层架构下的多表查询</h2><ol>\n<li><p>DGV额外增加列，每行单独添加数据</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>使用 DataGridView 显示数据</p>\n<ul>\n<li>设置 DataGridView 控件和各列（Columns）的属性</li>\n<li>设置 DataSource 属性，绑定数据源</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>DataGridView 各列的主要属性</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><strong>属性名称</strong></th>\n<th><strong>说明</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>HeaderText</td>\n<td>列标题文本</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Visible</td>\n<td>指定列是否可见</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>ReadOnly</td>\n<td>指定单元格是否为可读</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>DataPropertyName</td>\n<td>绑定的数据列的名称</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>DGV修改外键单元格类型展示类型为下拉框</p>\n<p>使用组合框栏的步骤：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>设置列的类型为：DataGridViewComboBoxColumn</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>设置属性DisplayStyle</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">cbo.DisplayStyle &#x3D; DataGridViewComboBoxDisplayStyle.ComboBox</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>绑定外键表数据</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">cbo.DisplayMember &#x3D; &quot;********&quot;;\ncbo.ValueMember &#x3D; &quot;********&quot;;\ncbo.DataSource &#x3D; *****;</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><p>设置 ReadOnly 属性值为 True</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>修改实体类，增加额外的实体作为辅助实例</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>实体类修改为关系型</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><ul>\n<li>使用 ComboBox 实现数据的联动显示</li>\n<li>使用辅助列显示关联表数据的步骤</li>\n<li>使用组合框栏显示关联表数据<ul>\n<li>先绑定主要数据，再通过外键属性值获取数据</li>\n<li>扩展实体类</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","text":"实体类在Windows程序中的高级应用三层架构下的多表查询 DGV额外增加列，每行单独添加数据 使用 DataGridView 显示数据 设置 DataGridView 控件和各列（Columns）的属性 设置 DataSource 属性，绑定数据源 DataGridView 各...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":684,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Study","slug":"Study","count":9,"path":"api/categories/Study.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Study","slug":"Study","count":9,"path":"api/tags/Study.json"},{"name":"C#","slug":"C","count":1,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"Winform","slug":"Winform","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Winform.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E4%BD%93%E7%B1%BB%E5%9C%A8Windows%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实体类在Windows程序中的高级应用</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%82%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E8%A1%A8%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">三层架构下的多表查询</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">总结</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"沐羽","slug":"沐羽","avatar":"https://tenapi.cn/qqimg/?qq=3106871518","link":"https://pigeonmuyz.github.io","description":"YOASOBI 永远的神！","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/pigenmuyz","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"占位文章7","uid":"7261ef05455bb29ecb9c8a255d3efc54","slug":"占位文章7","date":"2021-06-03T02:00:00.000Z","updated":"2021-06-03T02:41:54.980Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/占位文章7.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"1111 ","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":5,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Study","slug":"Study","count":9,"path":"api/categories/Study.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Study","slug":"Study","count":9,